data.description: Welcome to 1209 S 3rd Avenue, a remodeled 2,450 sq ft brick home in Yakima, Washington. With five bedrooms and two baths on nearly 1/4 acre, this residence offers spacious and comfortable living. The upper level boasts two inviting bedrooms, a remodeled kitchen, a naturally lit dining room, and a spacious living room with a cozy fireplace.Descending to the lower level, discover three generously sized bedrooms, a full bathroom, and a convenient laundry room. The family room, adorned with a gas stove, provides a warm space for relaxation. A dedicated study area adds versatility.The remodel in 2020 includes a new roof and additional attic insulation, plus double-pane windows ensuring energy efficiency and added comfort and longevity. Outside, a detached garage and several outbuildings offer ample storage. Whether you're a first-time buyer seeking assistance or an investor looking for financing flexibility, this property caters to your needs. This property is being sold as-is, in its present condition, offering you the perfect canvas to transform it into your dream home.
